trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 데이터를 제공는 <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved"> </xref> 이벤트입니다.
이 클래스는 상속 될 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] A tracking service that implements the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification> interface raises a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> event to notify the runtime tracking infrastructure that new instances of a particular workflow <xref:System.Type> should no longer be tracked.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]구현 하는 추적 서비스는 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification>발생 시키는 인터페이스는 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved>특정 워크플로의 새 인스턴스를 하는 런타임 추적 인프라에 알리는 이벤트를 <xref:System.Type>더 이상 추적 해야 합니다.</xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification>

trans-unit.source: The tracking service uses a ProfileRemovedEventArgs to provide the workflow <xref:System.Type> to the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: 추적 서비스는 ProfileRemovedEventArgs를 사용 하 여 워크플로 제공 <xref:System.Type>런타임 추적 인프라에.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> uses a ProfileRemovedEventArgs when it raises the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService.ProfileRemoved?displayProperty=fullName> event.
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어는 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>발생 시킬 때는 ProfileRemovedEventArgs를 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService.ProfileRemoved?displayProperty=fullName>이벤트.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService.ProfileRemoved?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>

trans-unit.source: After a tracking service raises the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> event, the runtime tracking infrastructure will no longer associate a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> with the specified workflow <xref:System.Type> for that tracking service.
trans-unit.target: 발생 한 후 추적 서비스는 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved>이벤트를 런타임 추적 인프라는 더 이상 연결 하지는 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>지정 된 워크플로 <xref:System.Type>해당 추적 서비스에 대 한.</xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs"></xref> class.

If you use this constructor when you raise a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> event inside a tracking service, you must explicitly set <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved>추적 서비스 내부 이벤트 명시적으로 설정 해야 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> 발생 시킬 때이 생성자를 사용 하는 경우

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs"></xref> class that applies to the specified workflow <xref:System.Type>.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs"> </xref> 지정된 된 워크플로 <xref:System.Type>.</xref:System.Type> 에 적용 되는 클래스

trans-unit.source: A new instance of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs> is created with <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> set to the specified <xref:System.Type>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs> <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A>지정 된 <xref:System.Type>.</xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> 사용 하 여 만든</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs> 의 새 인스턴스

trans-unit.source: The workflow <xref:System.Type> for which the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref> should be removed.
Gets or sets the workflow <xref:System.Type> for which the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref> should be removed.
trans-unit.target: 워크플로 가져오거나 설정 합니다. <xref:System.Type>입니다는 <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"> </xref> 제거 해야 합니다.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: WorkflowType specifies the workflow <xref:System.Type> for which a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> no longer exists, and which, therefore, should no longer be tracked by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: WorkflowType 지정 워크플로 <xref:System.Type>입니다는 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>더 이상 존재 하 고는, 따라서 더 이상 추적 해야 런타임 추적 인프라에서.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Type>
